{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-05219/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-05219"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:52:19"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["full shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["high"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["group shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A trio seated on a couch are surrounded by reporters."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05219/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-05219","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05219/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-05219"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05219/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05219/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05219/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05219/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05219/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05219/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05219/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05219/canvas/1/02e54833-bda4-412d-bb1c-e952c2b58e84","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T20:17:35.185Z","creator":"Tallulah Stallvik","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>A nineteenth-century painting of Roman ruins by French artist Antoine Claude Ponthus Cinier hangs above Barbara Rose and Rubio. Born in Lyon in 1812, Cinier was known for his vedute, or large-scale cityscape paintings. The artist spent several years in Rome in the 1840s, during which he produced a series of works depicting the city and its surrounding countryside.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05219/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:767.944054652882,22.775572378138556,585.5359121122599,334.17651403249624"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05219/canvas/1/dc1ce662-8f34-494a-82fc-6a4816fc6b25","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T20:18:02.186Z","creator":"Tallulah Stallvik","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>This staging of this scene emphasizes the performativity on display by Barbara Rose and her fiancé Rubio. They’re filmed by the camera and watched intently by all the reporters in the room. This moment is part of <em>Phantom Thread’s </em>fascination with questions of surface, social roles and cues, and, indeed, sincerity (or authenticity and openness). In this sense, as Reynolds and Alma continue growing as a couple and learning to be sincere with one other—in the twisted form that it takes—Barbara Rose and Rubio act as foils.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05219/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:614.9529172821286,376.6506646971932,382.7894202363367,299.03757385524375"}}}]}]}]}